title: Default values are not shown in Show Report Parameters' dialog
description: The default values for report parameters are not being displayed in the Show Report Parameters' dialog.
OB: When opening the Show Report Parameters' dialog, the default values for the report parameters are not visible.
EB: The default values for the report parameters should be displayed in the Show Report Parameters' dialog.
SR:
To reproduce this issue, follow these steps:
1. Create several report parameters and set default values for them.
2. Drag the report parameters to the layout.
3. Open the Show Report Parameters' dialog and check if the default values are displayed.
